Class IdHashSet

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
IdCollection, IdSet
public class IdHashSet
extends AbstractIdHashCollection
implements IdSet

Provides an implementation of IdSet based on a hash table. Uses double hashing. The table size is always a prime number.

You MUST NOT try to add Long.MAX_VALUE or Long.MIN_VALUE to the set, because these value are reserved for unused table entries.

This set is a lot faster than List<Long> and even a little bit faster than trove4j's implementation.
